# Main code
res = 0
for a in range(1, n+1):
    for b in range(a, n+1):
        c = a ^ b
        if c <= n and c >= b and c < (a+b) and a > (c-b) and b > (c-a):
            res += 1

print(res)

n = int(input())
ans = 0
for c in range(n, 1, -1):
    cs = [int(x) for x in "{:02b}".format(c)]
    if 0 not in cs or 1 not in cs[1:]:
        continue
    N = len(cs)
    for i in range(1, N-1):
        if cs[i]==0: continue
        for j in range(i+1, N):
            if cs[j]==1: continue
            left = 2**sum(cs[i+1:j])
            right = 2**(N-j-1)
            ans += left*right
print(ans)
